/a>购买。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/LIAM-GALLAGHER">Liam Gallagher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/BLINK-182">Blink-182</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gerry-cinnamon">Gerry Cinnamon</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen</a>也将成为今年的头条新闻。</p><p>他还将成为布达佩斯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fred-again-stormzy-sam-smith-and-martin-garrix-lead-stacked-line-up-for-sziget-2024-3557952">Sziget 音乐节</a>和赫尔辛基<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/flow-festival-announces-pulp-pj-harvey-the-smile-fred-again-and-more-for-stacked-2024-line-up-3547974">Flow 音乐节的</a>主角。</p><p>与此同时，Lil Yachty 一直忙于与众多艺术家合作。他最近发行了与摇滚明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yungblud">Yungblud</a>合作的歌曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-lil-yachty-when-we-die-can-we-still-get-high-3577419">When We Die (Can We Still Get High?)</a> ”，以及与童年好友<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/faye-webster">Faye Webster</a>合作的歌曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/faye-webster-announces-new-album-teams-up-with-lil-yachty-for-lego-ring-video-3570318">Lego Ring</a> ”。</p><p>去年，他还在专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-yachty-lets-start-here-fuck-any-of-the-albums-i-dropped-before-this-one-3410547">让我们从这里开始</a>》中令人惊讶地转向了迷幻摇滚。他谈到这张专辑时说：“有很多孩子没有听过我的任何参考文献。他们对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bon-iver">Bon Iver</a> 、平克·弗洛伊德、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑色安息日</a>或<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-brown">詹姆斯·布朗</a>一无所知。我想向人们展示我不同的一面——最重要的是我可以做任何事情。”</p><p>在其他新闻中，Yachty <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-yachty-says-hip-hop-is-in-a-terrible-place-right-now-3537060">谈到了嘻哈音乐的现状</a>，称这一流派“现在处于一个可怕的境地”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lil-yachty-perform-unreleased-track-stayinit-with-fred-again-3585644">观看 Lil Yachty 与 Fred 再次表演未发行的曲目“Stayinit”后，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
